2128.comment: Movement 1: a) Touch Button: touch four virtual buttons with right hand in the air (start left-right-diagonal left, down)

2133.comment: Movement 1: b) Touch Button: touch four virtual buttons with left hand in the air (start right-left-diagonal right, down)

2136.comment: Movement 2: a) Drag and Drop: drag with right hand in the air (start left-to right), drag with right hand in the air (start top to buttom), drag with right hand in the air (start front to chest)

2141.comment: Movement 2: b) Drag and Drop: drag with left hand in the air (start right to left); drag with left hand in the air (start top to buttom); drag with left hand in the air (start front to chest)

2148.comment: Movement 3: a) Zoom: zoom in with both hands (start front to side)

2151.comment: Movement 3: b) Zoom: zoom out with both hands diagnoal (start front to diagonal up/down)

2154.comment: Movement 4: a) Circular movement: with both hands, formed as fists, start in front of the person, form circles upwards two times

2158.comment: Movement 4: b) Circular movement: with both hands, formed as fists, start in front of the person, form circles downwards two times

2165.comment: Movement 5: a) Pick up Object: Pick up object with the left hand from the left side to the middle, switch hands, place object with right hand to the right side

2168.comment: Movement 5: b) Pick up Object: Pick up object with the right hand from the right to the middle, switch hands, place object with left hand to the left side

2176.comment: Movement 6: a) Movement: bend both lower arms 90° to the front

2181.comment: Movement 6: b) Movement: bend both whole arms 90° to the front

2183.comment: Movement 6: c) Movement: bend both whole arms 90° to the side

2187.comment: Movement 6: d) Movement: wave with lower arms next to the head two times

2193.comment: Movement 7: Mix: push two buttons with the right hand (middle-diagonal right), drag one object from front to chest, zoom in with both hands two times, push two buttons with the right hand (middle-diagonal right), form circles upwards two times, drag object from chest to front, push two buttons with the right hand (middle-diagonal right)
